  "detailed_description": [
    {
      "heading": "Ultra-Compact and Secure",
      "text": "The Ubiquiti G5 Turret Ultra is a compact and powerful security camera designed to blend seamlessly into your environment. Its tamper-resistant design deters vandalism, while its compact size blends seamlessly into your surroundings. With a weatherproof exterior, this camera can withstand the elements, providing reliable surveillance year-round. Unite exceptional video quality, discreet design, and advanced features with the Ubiquiti G5 Turret Ultra.  This versatile camera offers a powerful solution for securing your home or business."
    },
    {
      "heading": "Sharp Vision, Day or Night",
      "text": "Capture every detail with crisp 2K (4MP) video resolution. The camera boasts an ultra-wide viewing angle of 102.4 degrees, ensuring expansive coverage. Even in low-light conditions, the G5 Turret Ultra delivers exceptional clarity thanks to its long-range night vision that reaches up to 30 meters."
    },
    {
      "heading": "Intelligent Monitoring",
      "text": "The G5 Turret Ultra utilizes built-in AI capabilities to detect specific events, minimizing false alarms and allowing you to focus on what matters most. Additionally, the integrated microphone allows you to record audio for a more comprehensive security solution. The microphone could be disabled if needed. Power and data are delivered seamlessly through a single PoE cable, simplifying installation and eliminating the need for separate power outlets."
    }
  ],
